Read `docs/prd/mvp_scope_1.md` first to match shape. Cross-check scope against root `CLAUDE.md`'s Explicit MVP Exclusions and Current Development Phase before including anything — flag conflicts in an "Out of scope" section rather than omitting them silently. Save as `docs/prd/<kebab-case-name>-v1.md`; present as a draft awaiting human review, not approved scope.
